@startuml
actor Student
participant "Client App" as Client
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Topic Service" as TopicService
participant "GigaChat Service" as GigaChat
participant "Auth Service" as AuthService
participant "Bot Service" as BotService
participant "Database" as DB

== Generate Topics ==
Student -> Client: Initiates topic generation
Client -> Gateway: POST /api/topics/generate\n(X-Student-Guid, GenerateTopicRequest)
Gateway -> AuthService: Validate X-Student-Guid
AuthService --> Gateway: Validated studentGuid
Gateway -> TopicService: Forward POST /api/topics/generate
TopicService -> DB: Save UserRequest
DB --> TopicService: UserRequest saved
TopicService -> GigaChat: POST /generate\n(GigaMessageRequest)
GigaChat --> TopicService: GigaMessageResponse
TopicService -> TopicService: Parse response (TopicParser)
TopicService -> DB: Save GeneratedTopic(s)
DB --> TopicService: GeneratedTopic(s) saved
TopicService -> DB: Save TopicChangeLog
DB --> TopicService: TopicChangeLog saved
TopicService -> BotService: Send message\n(New topics generated for studentGuid)
BotService --> TopicService: Message sent
TopicService --> Gateway: GenerateTopic инструкция
Gateway --> Client: ResponseEntity<GenerateTopicResponse>
Client --> Student: Display generated topics

== Select Topic ==
Student -> Client: Selects a topic
Client -> Gateway: POST /api/topics/select\n(X-Student-Guid, SelectTopicRequest)
Gateway -> AuthService: Validate X-Student-Guid
AuthService --> Gateway: Validated studentGuid
Gateway -> TopicService: Forward POST /api/topics/select
TopicService -> DB: Find GeneratedTopic by topicId
DB --> TopicService: GeneratedTopic
TopicService -> DB: Check existing TopicSelection
DB --> TopicService: List<TopicSelection>
TopicService -> DB: Check active topics for studentGuid
DB --> TopicService: List<GeneratedTopic>
TopicService -> DB: Save TopicSelection
DB --> TopicService: TopicSelection saved
TopicService -> DB: Update GeneratedTopic status to PENDING
DB --> TopicService: GeneratedTopic updated
TopicService -> DB: Save TopicChangeLog
DB --> TopicService: TopicChangeLog saved
TopicService -> BotService: Send message\n(Topic selected: topicId, supervisorGuid)
BotService --> TopicService: Message sent
TopicService --> Gateway: Void
Gateway --> Client: ResponseEntity<Void>
Client --> Student: Confirm topic selection

@enduml